{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"lddt9unfhup1ewzugrh0wbr","title":"Stert","desc":"","updated":1691114152849,"created":1691075767723,"custom":{},"fname":"Dendron.started","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"9f2b161c7f7266e2c003b748f50fdf46","links":[],"anchors":{"安装":{"type":"header","text":"安装","value":"安装","line":12,"column":0,"depth":1},"初始化一个工作区":{"type":"header","text":"初始化一个工作区","value":"初始化一个工作区","line":16,"column":0,"depth":1},"添加一个新的markdown文件":{"type":"header","text":"添加一个新的markdown文件","value":"添加一个新的markdown文件","line":24,"column":0,"depth":1},"日历笔记":{"type":"header","text":"日历笔记","value":"日历笔记","line":39,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":[],"parent":"mhuw3kgnfehwkr17cv18g12","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"stert\">Stert<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#stert\"></a></h1>\n<p>Dendron  是一个vscode插件市场中的笔记软件，可以发布成静态网站。号称是专门给程序员用的笔记。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"安装\">安装<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#安装\"></a></h1>\n<p>首先需要有个VScode或者和VScode兼容的编辑器，然后在插件市场安装<a href=\"https://link.dendron.so/vscode\">Dendron</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"初始化一个工作区\">初始化一个工作区<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#初始化一个工作区\"></a></h1>\n<p>安装Dendron后可以看见下面的界面，点击 <code>Get Started </code>   如果没有看到此界面请在VScode 命令行输入 <code>Dendron：Launch</code></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>提示：VScode 命令行快捷键：<code>Ctrl+Shift+P </code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/image/Dendron.started/1691076460555.png\" alt=\"1691076460555\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"添加一个新的markdown文件\">添加一个新的markdown文件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#添加一个新的markdown文件\"></a></h1>\n<ol>\n<li>输入 <code>Ctrl+L / Cmd+L</code>打开查找栏。</li>\n<li>输入新便笺的名称。例如，您可以键入recipes</li>\n<li>单击“新建”。</li>\n<li>按Enter键。在系统中创建标题为recipes.md的新注释。您现在可以将内容添加到recipes笔记的正文中。</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p>提示：输入 <code>Ctrl+Tab / Cmd+Tab</code>快捷方式可返回到您正在查看的上一条注释。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>💡INFO：Dendron中的注释只是纯文本标记。备注：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在您的文件系统上本地运行。</li>\n<li>可跨操作系统和各种软件移植。</li>\n<li>使导入/导出更容易，包括将笔记发布到托管网站。</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"日历笔记\">日历笔记<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#日历笔记\"></a></h1>\n<p>安装Dendron后，VScode左下角有个 <code>CALENDAR VIEW</code>  ，可以通过点击日期创建日记。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/image/Dendron.started/1691077254557.png\" alt=\"1691077254557\"></p>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"","updated":1691107996619,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"b84c528db7c4d788406049268f5a99fb","links":[],"anchors":{},"children":["mhuw3kgnfehwkr17cv18g12","ds6ph3455vjc7l67mzntcs9","c1bs7wsjfbhb0zipaywqv1","ne0n46ryv85gh46x7s3zwqu","fzxc4lax935ogwcc4t5gzb8","9ijups7jdz7bum0n1pcgnw4"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"This is the root for your Dendron vault.\n\nIf you decide to publish your entire vault, it will be your landing page. You are free to customize any part of this page except the frontmatter at the top, between the `---`.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"task","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x",